oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Stereoselective inversion of gamma-vinyl-gamma-butyrolactone under palladium catalysis: application to the synthesis of (+)-exo- and (+)-endo-brevicomins
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: FERNANDES, RA
KATTANGURU, P
BETHI, V
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: WESTERN PINE BEETLE
ALLYLIC ALKYLATIONS
ENDO-BREVICOMIN
DERIVATIVES
ENANTIOMERS
ATTRACTANT
PHEROMONE
LACTONES
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An efficient gamma-epimerization of gamma-vinyl-gamma-butyrolactone is studied under palladium catalysis. The building blocks derived there in are used in an efficient stereoselective synthesis of (+)-exo- and (+)-endo-brevicomins.
